{"tid":225942,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"第50期六合彩討論","createTime":"2017-05-02T07:24:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T11:33:13.000Z","uid":41157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f2b40a906f95b0eb5e407575e8633b59e7347575","tid":225942,"uid":41157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T07:24:52.000Z","msg":"上期六合彩有一注中頭獎，二奬則只得0.5注中，今晚（2日）第50期有106萬左右多寶，馬會估計頭獎基金為800萬。<br />\n<br />\n雖然上期的七個開獎號碼總和僅得161，明顯以偏細分子的成績較好，但當中依然有一個4字頭大號碼入圍。<br />\n<br />\n翻查最近20期開獎紀錄，發覺它們在第45及46期落空後，至今三期均有出現，其間更共開七個之多，可見這次宜揀同類冧巴作為重心之選。<br />\n<br />\n44號最近曾於第30、36、38及44期先後四度攪出，除上名率不俗外，本身亦試過兩度隔五期後露面，今晚有機會以五跳格局重開，一於優先捧場。<br />\n<br />\n此外，48號在第30至49期之間共開六次，乃近20期內上名次數最多的4字頭一族，跟紅頂白可博其連下三城。"},{"pid":"022b383d60a779104431698eeaf36480a30e0138","tid":225942,"uid":41157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T07:27:46.000Z","msg":"大家有咩心水？<br />\n近期1號同4號狀態唔錯<br />\n冇開兩期之後慎防施回馬槍<br />\n可以做膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab46778f63fd773615947702bf030955500530f","tid":225942,"uid":76531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T08:52:35.000Z","msg":"我覺得跟住黎呢3期都可以喺1路號碼（10-19）<br />\n呢10個號碼當中選擇出3個或以上號碼,<br />\n理論上10個號碼開出3-7個（含特）嘅遺漏係6.17期<br />\n最近5次都喺理論遺漏內開出,而目前已經遺漏4期,<br />\n所以接下來三期（50,51,52）期，賭佢會再次喺理論遺漏內出。"},{"pid":"a28e4a7f31310babfa887df241d04ed050562d49","tid":225942,"uid":16372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T09:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70c6469c8fac60e1ed2b2477ab43ced7114edbd6","tid":225942,"uid":41157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T10:01:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得跟住黎呢3期都可以喺1路號碼（10-19）<br />\n呢10個號碼當中選擇出3個或以上號碼,<br />\n理論上10個號碼開出3-7個（含特）嘅遺漏係6.17期<br />\n最近5次都喺理論遺漏內開出,而目前已經遺漏4期,<br />\n所以接下來三期（50,51,52）期，賭佢會再次喺理論遺漏內出。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ecd27901055ebbc918dcffbbf5ff61da832f33a","tid":225942,"uid":41157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:14:44.000Z","msg":"原來近20期開左15期小<br />\n得5期大<br />\n特別號碼就14雙 6單"},{"pid":"4ed32b071f3b5c09abfd734ab025db75a43c83bc","tid":225942,"uid":76531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T13:53:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來近20期開左15期小<br />\n得5期大<br />\n特別號碼就14雙 6單</blockquote><br />\n凈係統計佢嘅次數,好難睇清楚佢嘅&quot;冷熱&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你試下好似咁樣記錄,特別號碼開出係大數就向上記錄.否則向下記錄.<br />\n如果上升證明大數處於&quot;熱&quot;,橫行代表&quot;溫&quot;,下降代表&quot;冷&quot;嘅狀態.<br />\n咁樣就可以好似股票咁樣技術分析喇.號碼處於咩狀態一目了然.<br />\n如果能在轉&ldquo;熱&ldquo;&rdquo;嘅初期就介入,一直買到佢狀態改變先放棄.正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/90v665B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F90v665B.png&h=4b81fd24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw,今晚1路一個都冇出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,仲有兩期."},{"pid":"f47f9dfd167310cc0fb3d4a33c369831c797fbb8","tid":225942,"uid":76531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T13:56:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家有咩心水？<br />\n近期1號同4號狀態唔錯<br />\n冇開兩期之後慎防施回馬槍<br />\n可以做膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n恭喜1號成功跑出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffada7b9ec13c6c9d1e430faadd348501309b5be","tid":225942,"uid":41157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:45:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大家有咩心水？<br />\n近期1號同4號狀態唔錯<br />\n冇開兩期之後慎防施回馬槍<br />\n可以做膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n恭喜1號成功跑出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可惜拖唔到腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c8c7caefc0d1b3af0d18388a3fb9242a4e482d","tid":225942,"uid":41157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:46:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>原來近20期開左15期小<br />\n得5期大<br />\n特別號碼就14雙 6單</blockquote><br />\n凈係統計佢嘅次數,好難睇清楚佢嘅&quot;冷熱&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你試下好似咁樣記錄,特別號碼開出係大數就向上記錄.否則向下記錄.<br />\n如果上升證明大數處於&quot;熱&quot;,橫行代表&quot;溫&quot;,下降代表&quot;冷&quot;嘅狀態.<br />\n咁樣就可以好似股票咁樣技術分析喇.號碼處於咩狀態一目了然.<br />\n如果能在轉&ldquo;熱&ldquo;&rdquo;嘅初期就介入,一直買到佢狀態改變先放棄.正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/90v665B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F90v665B.png&h=4b81fd24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw,今晚1路一個都冇出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,仲有兩期.</blockquote><br />\n可以一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3be156cdb58b383f4a70e8f430940bfa14695a44","tid":225942,"uid":41157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T13:56:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大家有咩心水？<br />\n近期1號同4號狀態唔錯<br />\n冇開兩期之後慎防施回馬槍<br />\n可以做膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n恭喜1號成功跑出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n1號呢排狀態大勇<br />\n成日開出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c5812889cc11f5f1c3a3b4116e3e994554e46f1","tid":225942,"uid":41157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T11:33:13.000Z","msg":"1號wp<br />\nq拖2 5 9"}]}